SCorpusRelationImpl
public interface SCorpusRelation
extends de.hu_berlin.german.korpling.saltnpepper.salt.saltCore.SRelation

This type represents a hierarchical relation between two corpora (two objects of type SCorpus). The source of this relation determines the super corpus and the target determines the sub corpus in the hierarchical relation.

The following features are supported:

  • SSuper Corpus
  • SSub Corpus
  • SCorpus Graph
